# Coding Standards

## Language

- Explanations to user: Simplified Chinese
- Code identifiers: English
- Code comments and docstrings: Simplified Chinese, PEP 257 style
- All functions/methods: type annotations required

## Change Discipline

- Minimal diff — no speculative features or abstractions
- One coherent task per session
- No error handling for impossible edge cases
- Match existing naming, import style, and patterns in surrounding code

## Monorepo Layout

| Package | Path | Framework |
|---------|------|-----------|
| `@navo/shared` | `shared/` | TypeScript types + i18n |
| `@navo/server` | `server/` | Express + ws + MySQL + Redis |
| `@navo/web` | `web/` | React + Vite + Tailwind + Zustand |
| Android | `android/` | Capacitor Gradle |

